    <section class="faq surface-muted" id="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="grid-12">
                <div class="md-col-6-centered">
                    <h2 class="text-center">FAQ</h2>
                    <h3 class="text-center">Common Questions</h3>

                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">Does SmartWeb work with my existing website?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">Yes. SmartWeb is installed as a widget — a small piece of code added to your existing site. It doesn't
                            require a rebuild. It works with WordPress, Wix, Webflow, custom sites, and most other platforms. We handle the
                            technical installation.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">What language does it support?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">SmartWeb can be configured for any language. For IWL clients in East Africa, we build in English and
                            Swahili by default. Multi-language setups are available on Convert and Close packages.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">What if a visitor asks something SmartWeb can't answer?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">The system is trained on your services, FAQs, and pricing — it handles the common questions confidently.
                            For anything outside its scope, it captures the enquiry and routes it to your team with the full conversation
                            context. No visitor gets a dead end.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">How long does setup take?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">Capture: 3–5 business days. Convert: 7–10 business days. Close: 2–3 weeks, depending on integration complexity.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">Do I need technical knowledge to manage it?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">No. The dashboard is built for business owners, not developers. You see conversations, lead details, and
                            notifications — no technical configuration required after launch.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">Can I use SmartWeb alongside SellFlow or BookingFlow?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">Yes — and this is where the system becomes most powerful. SmartWeb captures and qualifies leads from
                            your website. SellFlow and BookingFlow convert those leads on WhatsApp. Together, they cover the full journey
                            from first visit to confirmed payment.</p>
                    </details>
                    <details class="faq__item padding-l">
                        <summary class="faq__question">What happens after the 90-day guarantee period?</summary>
                        <p class="faq__answer">Nothing changes. The system keeps running. If you're on Convert or Close, we continue monthly
                            optimisation. You can also upgrade, expand to new pages, or add integrations as your business grows.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

